<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Register Konsumen WarungPOS</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Plus Jakarta Sans", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.18), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fbff 0%, #eef4ff 100%);
      color: #0f172a;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .shell {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1120px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(360px, 480px);
      border-radius: 32px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.14);
    }
    .brand {
      padding: 56px;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 45%, #bfdbfe 100%);
      color: #0f172a;
      position: relative;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
      color: #1d4ed8;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .brand h1 {
      margin: 20px 0 14px;
      font-size: 42px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    .brand p {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 470px;
      color: #334155;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .note-card {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
    }
    .note-card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .note-card p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #475569;
    }
    .panel {
      padding: 44px 40px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .back-link {
      color: #2563eb;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .panel h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      line-height: 1.15;
    }
    .panel-copy {
      margin: 10px 0 24px;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .message {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: #fef2f2;
      color: #b91c1c;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
    }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }
    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #334155;
    }
    input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border: 1px solid #dbe4f0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font: inherit;
      color: #0f172a;
      background: #f8fbff;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }
    input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #60a5fa;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.18);
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    button {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      font: inherit;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.22);
    }
    .auth-link {
      margin-top: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .auth-link a {
      color: #1d4ed8;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .shell { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .brand { display: none; }
      .panel { padding: 36px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="shell">
    <section class="brand">
      <span class="badge">Registrasi Konsumen</span>
      <h1>Buat akun pelanggan untuk memesan dari katalog WarungPOS.</h1>
      <p>Registrasi di halaman ini otomatis membuat akun dengan role `konsumen`. Jadi ini dipakai untuk pelanggan pembeli, bukan untuk pemilihan paket merchant atau onboarding pemilik usaha.</p>

      <div class="note-card">
        <h3>Penting</h3>
        <p>Paket `Free` dan `Pro` di landing page sebaiknya diarahkan ke proses sales atau onboarding merchant. Itu konsep langganan aplikasi, bukan role user transaksi di dalam aplikasi.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel">
      <a href="/" class="back-link">Kembali ke Landing Page</a>
      <h2>Daftar Akun Konsumen</h2>
      <p class="panel-copy">Isi data berikut untuk membuat akun pelanggan dan mulai menggunakan katalog pembelian.</p>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="message"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/register" method="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="nama">Nama</label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="nama"
            name="nama"
            value="<%= oldInput.nama %>"
            placeholder="Masukkan nama lengkap"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input
            type="email"
            id="email"
            name="email"
            value="<%= oldInput.email %>"
            placeholder="nama@email.com"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="password">Password</label>
          <input
            type="password"
            id="password"
            name="password"
            placeholder="Minimal 6 karakter"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="confirmPassword">Konfirmasi Password</label>
          <input
            type="password"
            id="confirmPassword"
            name="confirmPassword"
            placeholder="Ulangi password"
            required
          >
        </div>

        <button type="submit">Daftar Sekarang</button>
      </form>

      <p class="auth-link">
        Sudah punya akun? <a href="/login">Login di sini</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
